<p>2. Hansen, J., et al., Studies in humanized mice and convalescent humans yield a SARS-CoV-2 antibody cocktail. Science, 2020. 369(6506): p. 1010-1014. </p>
<p>3. Hassan, A.O., et al., A SARS-CoV-2 Infection Model in Mice Demonstrates Protection by Neutralizing Antibodies. Cell, 2020. 182(3): p. 744-753.e4. </p>
